<h2>Manuscript Submission</h2>

<p>It is essential that authors submit a <a href="/static/guidelines#presubmission" title="Go to presubmission guidelines">presubmission inquiry</a> before submitting a full paper. Presubmission inquiries allow authors to quickly find out whether their paper is likely to be broadly suitable for <em>PLOS Medicine</em>. To submit a presubmission inquiry please log on or register at our <a href="http://www.editorialmanager.com/pmedicine" title="Go to online submissin site">online submission site</a>. You will need to provide an abstract and a cover letter with up to ten key references from the study.</p>

